Package vallibrary.measures

Class Summary
AdjustedRand The Adjusted_Rand class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing Adjusted Rand Index.
Clest The Clest class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing CLEST measure.
ConsensusClustering The Consensus_Clustering class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing Consensus Cluster measure.
FigureOfMerit The Figure_Of_Merit is the base class for all FOM measures.
FIndex The FMeasure class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing F-Measure Index.
FMIndex The FMIndex class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing Fowlkes and Mallows Index.
GapStatistics The Gap_Statistics is the base class for all Gap statistics measures.
KrzanowskiLai The Krzanowski_and_Lai is the base class for all KL measures.
Measure The Measure class is the base class for all measures.
NullMeasure The Null_Measure class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states informations for computing Null Measure.
Silhouette The Adjusted_Rand class provides an object that encapsulates methods and states information for computing Adjusted Rand Index.
WithinClustersSumSquares The Within_Clusters_Sum_Squares is the base class for all WCSS measures.
